{
  "stem": "7455.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He's hesitant of giving it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he thinks, let somebody else give who's richer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had a hard time collecting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when they did not collect the amount that they expected, they took 50 men and shot them in the marketplace as a warning that if their demands are not met, that's what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Naturally now, whoever had it, whatever you had, you gave to save lives.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We didn't have much to give with my father because of our fire and so on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But whatever we had, we gave some.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And some of it-- my father had friend, a Polish friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a man, a couple.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Kocian was their name, a lifetime friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we brought some things that were saved from the fire to them to hold it for us, that if a time comes when were are starving, where our life depends on buying a loaf of bread or something, that we should have something.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because if we have it with us, the Germans may barge in and take it away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We need some material things for our future safety.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We don't know what tomorrow brings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the killing of those people, everybody gave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the time came and that demand was met, it was quiet for some time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After a certain time, they came with other demands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They even wanted thoroughbred horses, so men who for-- where does a Jew know about thoroughbred horses?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to find connections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were some people who were very capable and who could organize.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did [? a little ?] [? bit. ?] Unbelievable demands that was given-- money, gold-- money, Polish money, was not much of value-- just valuables, gold, silver, to pacify them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then my cousin [?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
